were holding hands?

631
00:34:16,281 --> 00:34:17,807
Yeah.

632
00:34:18,005 --> 00:34:21,440
Sounds like Harlan and Reina were close.

633
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:24,156
Close enough Sealey
should've mentioned her.

634
00:34:24,394 --> 00:34:26,054
He knew she was at those meetings.

635
00:34:26,054 --> 00:34:28,030
So he's covering for her.

636
00:34:28,030 --> 00:34:29,414
But why?

637
00:34:31,454 --> 00:34:33,274
You had the pick of the crop,

638
00:34:33,274 --> 00:34:35,117
