639
00:34:35,449 --> 00:34:38,326
With Elliot, Harlan.

640
00:34:38,326 --> 00:34:39,259
What do you mean?

641
00:34:39,259 --> 00:34:41,501
But you also had a problem.

642
00:34:41,501 --> 00:34:43,461
If you were named, you'd be deported.

643
00:34:43,461 --> 00:34:44,690
Yes.

644
00:34:44,690 --> 00:34:47,419
Yeah. Forgot to mention that.

645
00:34:47,419 --> 00:34:48,720
How is that relevant?

646
00:34:48,720 --> 00:34:51,782
I'm guessing that's why
you loved Elliot so much.

647
00:34:51,782 --> 00:34:53,631
Why you couldn't allow him
to name you.

648
00:34:53,631 --> 00:34:55,575
You were looking out for number one.

649
00:34:55,575 --> 00:34:59,262
I would have gone to Siberia
if Elliot asked me to.

650
00:34:59,262 --> 00:35:01,678
Yet you were cozying up
to Harlan Sealey,

651
00:35:01,678 --> 00:35:04,002
not a mile from where
Elliot was killed.

652
00:35:04,002 --> 00:35:06,445
If I was so scared of being deported,

653
00:35:06,445 --> 00:35:08,118
I would have married Harlan.

654
00:35:08,118 --> 00:35:09,439
Did he ask you?

655
00:35:09,439 --> 00:35:10,547
Yes.

656
00:35:11,948 --> 00:35:13,550
But he was a...

657
00:35:13,550 --> 00:35:16,337
he was a man of words.

658
00:35:17,292 --> 00:35:20,693
I wanted the real thing.

659
00:35:20,693 --> 00:35:22,789
You wanted Elliot.

660
00:35:25,653 --> 00:35:27,538
Did Harlan know that?

661
00:35:27,538 --> 00:35:29,690
It was obvious.

662
00:35:31,454 --> 00:35:33,544
And he knew Elliot might
give your name to the committee,

663
00:35:33,544 --> 00:35:36,734
sending you back to Prague.

664
00:35:48,595 --> 00:35:51,694
You gave us a lot, Mr. Sealey.

665
00:35:51,694 --> 00:35:54,474
Names from the meetings,

666
00:35:54,474 --> 00:35:56,692
a dirty cop... / all of whom are dead.

667
00:35:56,692 --> 00:35:58,006
And innocent.

668
00:35:58,006 --> 00:36:00,040
But thanks, anyway.

669
00:36:00,040 --> 00:36:02,838
I'm sorry nothing panned out.

670
00:36:02,838 --> 00:36:06,473
Well, Reina Kraus is still around,

671
00:36:06,473 --> 00:36:08,751
but you didn't mention her.

672
00:36:08,751 --> 00:36:11,741
Reina had nothing to do
with Elliot's death.

673
00:36:11,741 --> 00:36:12,949
But she did.

674
00:36:12,949 --> 00:36:14,184
She was the reason.

675
00:36:14,184 --> 00:36:16,627
You wanted to marry her.

676
00:36:17,392 --> 00:36:21,874
I plead guilty to being
a young man in love.

677
00:36:22,651 --> 00:36:25,478
Must've hurt knowing
she loved Elliot.

678
00:36:25,478 --> 00:36:26,937
What about Harlan, here?

679
