Rosenberg are dead.

702
00:37:53,718 --> 00:37:55,631
So terrible.

703
00:37:59,171 --> 00:38:02,705
It's too bad that Elliot
didn't make it tonight.

704
00:38:02,705 --> 00:38:04,947
He has a lot on his mind.

